abstract: Ha Na Jang maintains one-stroke lead following first round of the LPGA Tour's Marathon Classic.
lead_paragraph: Ha Na Jang birdied the par-5 18th for a five-under-par 66 and a one-stroke lead through the first round of the L.P.G.A. Tour’s Marathon Classic

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Golf; Jang Leads L.P.G.A. Event
